# Motor Control Firmware Directory

This directory contains motor control code for the Pololu G2 motor drivers.

## Files to be added:
- motor_driver.py - Main motor control class
- kinematics.py - Omnidirectional drive kinematics
- pid_controller.py - PID control implementation
- test_motor_direction.py - Motor direction testing script
- calibrate_encoders.py - Encoder calibration
- calibrate_speed.py - Speed calibration
- tune_pid.py - PID tuning utility
- calibrate_kinematics.py - Kinematic calibration
